// Secrets.example.xcconfig
//
// Template for build-time secrets. To configure a local build:
//
//   1. Copy this file to `Secrets.xcconfig` (same directory, repo root).
//   2. Fill in your Adzuna API credentials below.
//
// `Secrets.xcconfig` is gitignored — it never gets committed. It is the app
// target's base configuration; the values are injected into the app's Info.plist
// (AdzunaAppID / AdzunaAppKey) at build time via $(ADZUNA_APP_ID) / $(ADZUNA_APP_KEY)
// substitution, and read at runtime by BundleAppConfig.
//
// Get free-tier credentials at https://developer.adzuna.com/
//
// Note: `//` starts a comment in xcconfig — keep values clear of it. Adzuna keys
// are hex, so they're safe.

ADZUNA_APP_ID =
ADZUNA_APP_KEY =
